cu.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an invalid value will cause the ASN.1 parser to fail initialization and prevent proper message encoding/decoding.

du.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an invalid value will cause the ASN.1 parser to fail initialization and prevent proper message encoding/decoding.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為無效值將導致 ASN.1 解析器初始化失敗，並阻止正確的消息編碼/解碼。
